I
I, Sora swear to respect and carry out the way of the ctberninja in all my best affairs. Ishall keep the guilds best interest in my thoughts always, my honor shall be defended at any cost. I will carry myself in this manner always, or forever be banished from this great oppurtunity. my sensei is soudgarden
